Name: 3 vs 3 Honorable Battlefield
Description:
A real-time 3 vs 3 battle.
Play alone or with exceptional party members to become the best on the Honorable Battlefield.
TipText: You can either play alone or in a party on the Honorable Battlefield.

Name: 5 vs 5 Courageous Battlefield
Description:
A real-time 5 vs 5 battle.
Play alone or with exceptional party members to become the best on the Honorable Battlefield.
TipText: You can either play alone or in a party on the Courageous Battlefield.
